trans-unit.source: Provides an interface to allow a composite-control designer to recreate the child controls of its associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller ett gränssnitt för att tillåta en sammansatt kontroll designer att återskapa de underordnade kontrollerna för den associerade kontrollen i designläge.

trans-unit.source: A class derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl> implements the ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor interface to allow its associated designer to call the control's <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> method at design time.
trans-unit.target: En klass som härletts från <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl>implementerar gränssnittet ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor så att dess associerade designer att anropa kontrollens <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A>metoden vid designtillfället.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor.RecreateChildControls%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl>

trans-unit.source: The associated designer must derive from <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Associerade designern måste vara härledd från <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.CompositeControlDesigner>

trans-unit.source: The ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor interface is used primarily by control developers.
trans-unit.target: Gränssnittet ICompositeControlDesignerAccessor används främst av control-utvecklare.

trans-unit.source: In a control derived from <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl"></xref>, recreates the child controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: I en kontroll som härletts från <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompositeControl"> </xref>, återskapas de underordnade kontrollerna i designläge.

trans-unit.source: Called by the control's associated designer.
The RecreateChildControls method allows a designer for a composite control to recreate the control's child controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RecreateChildControls tillåter en designer för en sammansatt kontroll att återskapa dess underordnade kontroller vid designtillfället.

trans-unit.source: The RecreateChildControls method is used primarily by control developers.
trans-unit.target: Metoden RecreateChildControls används främst av control-utvecklare.
